idCitation.resTitle: Toronto District School Board school locations

Consts.useLimit: Source must be credited. Cannot be re-sold The data does not identify special purpose schools such as vocational training schools or adult education schools. The data also is best used when it is overlaid with the City of Toronto's street and address coverage.

dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data set is a shape file that contains the location of the Toronto District Schools. The data is collected and maintained by the Planning Division of the Toronto District School Board in order to support daily operations at the Board.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: The Data is an ESRI Shape File (point)
